Text: Forrester ResearchKim My name is Molly Vaughan and I work along side your Forrester Account Manager David Kobierowski to cover the relationship between Forrester and Enron I was hoping for an opportunity to have a minute conversation with you to find out more about your specific role and business challenges that you may be facing Based on that conversation I will be in a better position to direct you to some of the research we have that addresses those specific topics Let me know when a good time for me to call would be Link to Forresters homepage HomeFFhtml I look forward to working with you Best regards Molly Vaughan Molly Vaughan Forrester Research Inc Technology Sq Cambridge MA Direct email Corporate Web site wwwforrestercom
